    "retreat_destinations_AKtM4t": {
      "type": "retreat-destinations",
      "blocks": {
        "destination_DRCBPi": {
          "type": "destination",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7.jpg",
            "quota": "",
            "location": "Hawaii & Napa Valley, CA",
            "title": "Preparing the Bride: A Sacred Immersion",
            "description": "Preparing the Bride: A Sacred Immersion\n\nBeyond the Veil. Before the Vow. Become the Dream.\n\nThe world prepares you for a wedding; the House of Vuu prepares you for a Legacy.\n\nIn the whirlwind of logistics, guest lists, and expectations, the most important element can often be eclipsed: You. Before you are a wife, a partner, or a hostess, you are a woman of infinite worth, fashioned with a specific soul-signature.\n\nPreparing the Bride is a definitive, multi-dimensional immersion designed to anchor your identity and celebrate the woman behind the white dress. This is your sanctuary—a space to be seen, honored, and celebrated for who you are, not just for the occasion you are hosting.\n\nThe Internal Architecture: Honoring the Woman\nThrough a curated blend of spiritual anchoring and emotional recalibration, we awaken the Dreamer within. We believe a sacred union is not where your individual dreams go to die, but where they are catalyzed.\n\nThis is where you silence the noise of the \"event\" to hear the rhythm of your own heart. We deconstruct the fear of \"losing yourself\" in union and replace it with an unshakeable security in your unique brilliance. You are not losing your identity; you are expanding it.\n\nDonning the Mantle of Authority\nThis is your season of elevation. You will be guided to move past the role of \"fiancée\" and step into your Mantle of Grace. You will leave refreshed, elevated, and anchored—carrying a sense of self-honor that will fuel your marriage for decades to come.\n\nYou are more than a bride; you are a woman fashioned for a Kingdom. It is time to celebrate the Queen.",
            "content_subtitle": "<p>Beyond the Veil. Before the Vow. Become the Dream.</p>",
            "paragraph_1": "<p>The world prepares you for a wedding; the <strong>House of Vuu</strong> prepares you for a <strong>Legacy</strong>.</p><p>In the whirlwind of guest lists and logistics, the most vital element is often eclipsed: <strong>You.</strong> Before you are a wife, a partner, or a hostess, you are a woman of infinite worth, fashioned with a specific soul-signature. This is your sanctuary—a space to be seen, honored, and celebrated for the woman you are, not just the occasion you are hosting.</p>",
            "paragraph_2": "<h3><strong>Anchor Your Identity</strong></h3><p><strong>Your wedding is a day; your identity is forever.</strong> We believe a sacred union is not where your individual dreams go to die, but where they are catalyzed. Within this private mountain sanctuary, we silence the noise of the \"event\" to amplify the rhythm of your heart. You aren’t losing your identity in marriage; you are expanding it.</p>",
            "paragraph_3": "<h3><strong>The Architecture of Grace</strong></h3><p>Through a curated blend of spiritual anchoring and emotional recalibration, we deconstruct the fear of \"losing yourself\" and replace it with an unshakeable security in your unique brilliance. You will be guided to:</p><ul><li><strong>Deconstruct</strong> the pressure of the \"event\" to focus on the magnitude of your union.</li><li><strong>Awaken</strong> the Dreamer within, ensuring your personal calling thrives alongside your joint mandate.</li><li><strong>Architect</strong> an internal \"Blueprint of Grace\" that will define your presence as a wife and a partner.</li></ul>",
            "paragraph_4": "<h3><strong>Don the Mantle</strong></h3><p>This is your season of elevation. Move past the role of \"fiancée\" and step into your <strong>Mantle of Grace and Authority.</strong> You will leave refreshed, anchored, and carrying a sense of self-honor that will fuel your marriage for decades to come.</p>",
            "paragraph_5": "<p></p><p></p>",
            "cta_text": "Apply for Alignment",
            "cta_link": "",
            "cta_new_tab": false,
            "modal_trigger": true
          }
        },
        "destination_h4AgrP": {
          "type": "destination",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4.jpg",
            "quota": "",
            "location": "Napa Valley, Ca",
            "title": "The Masterpiece Bride: The Couture Soul Immersion",
            "description": "The Internal Awakening. The External Coronation. Your Legacy, Tailored.\n\nFor the woman who understands that her wedding day is more than an event—it is a coronation.\n\nThe Masterpiece Immersion is the ultimate high-level experience for the bride who desires her internal transformation to be woven into the very fabric of her wedding day. This is an exclusive 5-day private residency in our Napa Valley sanctuary, where the evolution of your soul meets the artistry of high couture.\n\nYou will not just \"find\" a dress here. You will co-design the Mantle of your New Season alongside Nancy Vuu.\nThe Creative Communion\n\nIn this higher-level retreat, the \"Preparing the Bride\" immersion is expanded into a collaborative Design Lab. As you awaken the Dreamer within and anchor your identity in the truth that you are Fashioned for Love and Greatness, those insights are translated into sketches, textures, and silhouettes.\n\nThrough this intimate co-design process, Nancy Vuu captures the frequency of your highest self and anchors it into a bespoke bridal gown. Every stitch becomes a testament to your purpose; every layer of lace a reflection of your grace.\nThe Transformation\n\nYou will leave this sanctuary not only with a clear heart and a secure spirit but with the blueprint of a garment that reflects the Queen you have become. This is for the bride who wants to walk toward her future in a gown that was born from her own awakening.\n\nDo not just wear a design. Wear your destiny.\nTHE ELEVATED EXPERIENCE:\n\n    The Sacred Immersion: The complete physical, emotional, and spiritual recalibration to anchor your highest identity and secure your dreams within your union.\n\n    The Co-Design Atelier: Private, one-on-one design sessions with Nancy Vuu to architect your bespoke bridal gown from concept to couture sketch.\n\n    Fabric & Soul Pairing: A sensory exploration of world-class textiles, selecting the materials that best represent the \"Mantle\" you are preparing to don.\n\n    The Masterpiece Blueprint: You walk away with your custom design finalized, your measurements secured, and the peace of knowing your gown is being handcrafted by master artisans who know your story.\n\n    Couture Sanctuary: All-inclusive lodging, bespoke nourishment, and restorative treatments designed to prepare your body for the season ahead.",
            "content_subtitle": "<p>Your Presence Elevated. Your Vision Handcrafted.</p>",
            "paragraph_1": "<p>The world prepares you for a wedding; the <strong>House of Vuu</strong> prepares you for a <strong>Legacy</strong>.</p><p>In the whirlwind of guest lists and floor plans, it’s easy to lose the woman at the center of it all: <strong>You.</strong> Before you are a wife or a hostess, you are a woman of infinite worth. The <em>Masterpiece Bride</em> is our most exclusive 5-day sanctuary—a rare chance to step away from the performance and rediscover the woman behind the white dress.</p>",
            "paragraph_2": "<h3><strong>The Inner Atelier: Your Presence Elevated</strong></h3><p><strong>Quiet the noise. Find your glow.</strong><br/>Before we ever touch a sketchpad, we focus on your heart.</p><p><strong>Step Out of the Performance:</strong> Leave the to-do lists behind. We provide a private mountain sanctuary where you can simply <em>be</em>.</p><p><strong>The Blueprint of Joy:</strong> Define the woman you are becoming. We believe a beautiful marriage isn’t where your dreams go to sleep—it’s where they truly wake up.</p><p><strong>Radiate from Within:</strong> Move past the role of \"fiancée\" to find the unshakeable confidence that comes from being fully present. You won't just look beautiful; you will feel powerful.</p><h3></h3>",
            "paragraph_3": "<h3><strong>The Masterpiece Blueprint: A Creative Partnership</strong></h3><p><strong>Co-Design Your Legacy with Nancy Vuu.</strong><br/>This is the heart of the immersion—where your internal peace meets the hands of a master designer.</p><ul><li><strong>The Co-Design Experience:</strong> Sit side-by-side with Nancy Vuu to bring your vision to life. Together, you will co-design your <strong>bespoke wedding gown and matching heirloom veil.</strong> This is more than a fitting; it’s a collaboration. Your pieces are handcrafted by master artisans who don’t just know your measurements—they know your heart.</li><li><strong>Total Peace of Mind:</strong> Leave the sanctuary with your design finalized, your measurements secured, and the confidence of knowing your vision is in the most capable hands in the world.</li></ul><h3></h3>",
            "paragraph_4": "<h3><strong>The Sanctuary: Restored and Ready</strong></h3><p><strong>Peace as your Foundation.</strong><br/>A Queen must be nourished to lead. We curate every detail of your restoration:</p><ul><li><strong> Bespoke Living:</strong> Private, all-inclusive mountain lodging designed for deep rest.</li><li><strong>Bespoke Nourishment:</strong> Organic, chef-curated cuisine tailored to your health and vitality.</li><li><strong>Restorative Care:</strong> From creative sessions to body treatments, every moment is designed to settle your nervous system. You will leave refreshed, radiant, and ready to enter your new chapter with grace.</li></ul>",
            "paragraph_5": "<h3>\"The world sees the Bride. We see the Woman. Walk into your forever, beautifully anchored.\"</h3>",
            "cta_text": "Apply for Alignment",
            "cta_link": "",
            "cta_new_tab": false,
            "modal_trigger": true
          }
        },
        "destination_Mrjdri": {
          "type": "destination",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_45_x_50_in_6.jpg",
            "quota": "",
            "location": "Napa Valley, CA",
            "title": "Women CEO: Dress The Dream",
            "description": "Where Strategy Meets Style.  This retreat moves from the high-stakes \"Boardroom\" energy into the \"Atelier\" energy—where the atmosphere is lighter, the connections are deeper, and the creativity is boundless.\n\nThis is for the woman who has already \"arrived\" but wants to remember how to play, dream, and belong.\n\nThey say it’s lonely at the top—but it doesn’t have to be.\n\nThe CEO Sanctuary is an exquisite, lighthearted immersion designed for the woman at the helm. This is a space where the \"Weight of the Crown\" is replaced by the \"Mantle of Authority.\" It is a four-day celebration of high-level sisterhood, strategic alignment, and the unapologetic freedom to dream even bigger than you already have.\n\nHere, we don’t just network; we champion. We don’t just plan; we play. This is your invitation to step out of the \"Command\" and into the \"Creative\"—surrounded by a circle of peers who speak your language and celebrate your magnitude.\nThe Collective Dream\n\nWhile the world asks for your results, we ask for your Dreams. In this strategic but soulful environment, you will find the \"White Space\" your calendar usually denies you. Through curated alignments and visionary sessions, you will connect with other CEO-level women to spark new ideas, forge high-level friendships, and realize that your next level of influence is best achieved together.\nThe Masterpiece Wardrobe: Your Mantle of Authority\n\nThe highlight of this sanctuary is the literal \"Couture of the Self.\" In a series of collaborative design labs, you will work with Nancy Vuu to architect your own Bespoke Wardrobe.\n\nThis isn't just shopping; it is the creation of your Mantle of Authority. You will co-design the garments that reflect your current power and your future destiny—pieces that tell the world exactly who you are before you ever speak a word.\n\nTHE EXPERIENCE: Joy, Strategy, and Style\n\n    Champion Circles: Lighthearted but high-level strategic alignment sessions where women leaders troubleshoot, brainstorm, and champion each other’s upcoming \"Big Moves.\"\n\n    The Design Atelier: A private, collaborative experience where you co-design a capsule of bespoke pieces—including your definitive \"Mantle of Authority\" (a signature power suit, coat, or gown).\n\n    The Freedom Lab: Creative workshops designed to awaken the \"Dreamer\" and find the freedom to pivot, expand, or simply enjoy your success.\n\n    Couture Connections: Curated social hours, mountaintop toasts, and \"Legacy Dinners\" designed to turn high-level contacts into lifelong friends.\n\n    The Restoration Suite: Napa Valley lodging, bespoke cuisine, and wellness experiences that prioritize \"Rest as a Strategy.\"",
            "content_subtitle": "<p>Women CEO: Dress The Dream</p>",
            "paragraph_1": "<p>Where Strategy Meets Style.  This retreat moves from the high-stakes \"Boardroom\" energy into the \"Atelier\" energy—where the atmosphere is lighter, the connections are deeper, and the creativity is boundless.<br/><br/><strong>This is for the woman who has already \"arrived\" but wants to remember how to play, dream, and belong.</strong></p>",
            "paragraph_2": "<p>The CEO Sanctuary is an exquisite, lighthearted immersion designed for the woman at the helm. This is a space where the \"Weight of the Crown\" is replaced by the \"Mantle of Authority.\" It is a four-day celebration of high-level sisterhood, strategic alignment, and the unapologetic freedom to dream even bigger than you already have.<br/><br/>Here, we don’t just network; we champion. We don’t just plan; we play. This is your invitation to step out of the \"Command\" and into the \"Creative\"—surrounded by a circle of peers who speak your language and celebrate your magnitude.<br/>The Collective Dream</p>",
            "paragraph_3": "<p>While the world asks for your results, we ask for your Dreams. In this strategic but soulful environment, you will find the \"White Space\" your calendar usually denies you. Through curated alignments and visionary sessions, you will connect with other CEO-level women to spark new ideas, forge high-level friendships, and realize that your next level of influence is best achieved together.<br/>The Masterpiece Wardrobe: Your Mantle of Authority<br/><br/>The highlight of this sanctuary is the literal \"Couture of the Self.\" In a series of collaborative design labs, you will work with Nancy Vuu to architect your own Bespoke Wardrobe.</p>",
            "paragraph_4": "<p>This isn't just shopping; it is the creation of your Mantle of Authority. You will co-design the garments that reflect your current power and your future destiny—pieces that tell the world exactly who you are before you ever speak a word.</p>",
            "paragraph_5": "<p>THE EXPERIENCE: Joy, Strategy, and Style.<br/><br/>    Champion Circles: Lighthearted but high-level strategic alignment sessions where women leaders troubleshoot, brainstorm, and champion each other’s upcoming \"Big Moves.\"<br/><br/>    The Design Atelier: A private, collaborative experience where you co-design a capsule of bespoke pieces—including your definitive \"Mantle of Authority\" (a signature power suit, coat, or gown).<br/><br/>    The Freedom Lab: Creative workshops designed to awaken the \"Dreamer\" and find the freedom to pivot, expand, or simply enjoy your success.<br/><br/>    Couture Connections: Curated social hours, mountaintop toasts, and \"Legacy Dinners\" designed to turn high-level contacts into lifelong friends.<br/><br/>Napa Valley lodging, bespoke cuisine, and wellness experiences that prioritize \"Rest as a Strategy.\"</p>",
            "cta_text": "Apply for Alignment",
            "cta_link": "",
            "cta_new_tab": false,
            "modal_trigger": true
          }
        }
      },
